com.yworks.yfiles.view

Interface IGraphSelection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEnumerable<IModelItem>, ISelectionModel<IModelItem>, Iterable<IModelItem>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphSelection

    public interface IGraphSelection
extends ISelectionModel<IModelItem>
    Manages the selection state of items in an IGraph instance.

    This interface provides access to the ISelectionModel instances that manage the selection of nodes, edges, labels, ports, and bends. The generic methods that use IModelItem parameters delegate to the corresponding domain-specific selection models.

    See Also:
    ISelectionModel
